msgstr "GRUBは、パスフレーズを入力するときに「私たち」キーボードが使用されていると仮定しています。 For this reason, if during installation you use an other keyboard map, before asking the passphrase the installer will set the keyboard map to \"us\", and after having recorded it restore the previously used one. In this case the installer will also spell each typed character of the passphrase, as it may differ from the one written on the key."

